If you are 2, 3, 4, 5 small guilds and want to team up to kill Manaetic Behemoth, Aerin Darr, Grummus, Terris Thule, Keeper of Sorrows, Saryrn, all 3 HoH trials, Mithaniel Marr, Bertoxxulous, Agnarr: go right ahead. Nothing is stopping you from doing so. The ONLY thing is, that you will not get any backflags from the guilds that ARE in the *Semi official agreement*. <br>
<br>
But the teaming up stops right there. To be Elemental flagged you still need Tallon Zek, Vallon Zek and Rallos Zek the Warlord, and for full elemental access you also need Solusek Ro. Those 4 mobs however happen to be on rotation. So if you team up on those, you ARE in violation of the rules of the RTA (presuming ofcourse you are, or one of the guilds you are teaming up with is, on at least one of the other rotations or is a posting entity).<br>
<br>
So, will teaming up get you into elementals? No it will not.<br>
<br>
Ok, then we make an official alliance for just TZ, VZ, RZtW and Sol Ro. HELLOO!!?? THIS now is exactly why was stated: If you team up for those, then the teaming parties ARE considered to be ONE alliance/posting entity for ALL rotations/planes.<br>
<br>
So instead of 5 small guilds on Severilous, we now have 1 alliance, made out of 5 guilds, on the Severilous rotation. Instead of having to wait 6 months for your turn on Sev, you now wait 5 months, BUT you get only 1 shot for your alliance, and not 5 for 5 separate guilds.<br>
<br>
Well, then we break our alliance again once we are elemental flagged. Every single guild that was in the former alliance kills the rotation mob on its own, and now that we are in elementals that should be cake. All get back on rotations and we live happily ever after.<br>
WRONG! ALL elemental planes, rings, named mobs of any importance, are on rotation as well. So now you are elemental flagged and you cannot do anything there but grind some exp and AA's.<br>
Yes that can be fun for some time. Just as much fun as it is in Plane of Tactics day in, day out all day long. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Kenau Kamikaze, Coercer of VoF ,  Levlenna, Archon of VoF. Guildleader.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shariona>Shariona</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mirth's Virtue - Guild Rep</span><br>  Posts: 255<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(12/9/03 7:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=501.topic&index=55>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Terror Australis</span><hr size=1> IF you team up on FLAG MOBS, you will be expected to keep that alliance FOR ALL the Rotations you are in.<br>
